@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "YOPO (Python)" {
  [cli.py] as CLI
  [schema.py] as SCHEMA

  package "policy" {
    [YopoNetwork] as NET
    [YopoTrainer] as TRAIN
    [YOPODataset] as DSET
    [LatticePrimitive] as LATTICE
    [StateTransform] as SXFORM

    package "models" {
      [ResNet18 / YopoBackbone] as BACKBONE
      [YopoHead] as HEAD
    }
  }

  package "loss" {
    [YOPOLoss] as LOSS_MAIN
    [SmoothnessLoss] as SMOOTH
    [GuidanceLoss] as GUIDE
    [SafetyLoss] as SAFE
    [compute_esdf (GPU/CPU)] as ESDF
  }

  [config/traj_opt.yaml] as YAML_CFG
}

package "Controller (ROS)" {
  component "so3_quadrotor_simulator" as QUAD_SIM {
    [quadrotor_simulator_so3] as QUAD_SIM_NODE
    [Quadrotor (dynamics)] as QUAD_DYN
  }

  component "so3_control" as SO3_CTRL {
    [network_control_node] as NET_CTRL_NODE
    [SO3ControlNodelet] as SO3_NODELET
    [SO3Control (geometric PD)] as SO3_ALGO
    [HGDO] as HGDO
    [NetworkControl] as NET_CTRL
  }
}

package "Simulator (ROS/CUDA)" {
  [sensor_simulator (CPU)] as SENS_SIM_CPU
  [sensor_simulator_cuda] as SENS_SIM_CUDA
  [CUDA raycast kernels] as CUDA_KERN
  [Maps (procedural env)] as MAP_GEN
}

package "docker/data-gen (no ROS)" as DG {
  [dataset_generator] as DG_BIN
  [CUDA raycast kernels] as DG_CUDA
  [Maps (procedural)] as DG_MAPS
}

' Dependencies
CLI --> SCHEMA
CLI --> TRAIN : cmd_train / cmd_sweep
CLI --> NET : cmd_trt
CLI --> DSET : cmd_visualize

TRAIN --> NET : constructs & trains
TRAIN --> DSET : dataloaders
TRAIN --> LOSS_MAIN : compute loss

NET --> BACKBONE : depth feature
NET --> HEAD : concat obs+img -> endstate+score
NET --> SXFORM : normalise / denormalise

SXFORM --> LATTICE : primitive grid

LOSS_MAIN --> SMOOTH : jerk & acc QP
LOSS_MAIN --> GUIDE : goal similarity
LOSS_MAIN --> SAFE : ESDF collision cost
SAFE --> ESDF : GPU / CPU EDT

NET_CTRL_NODE --> NET_CTRL
NET_CTRL --> SO3_ALGO : calculateControl
NET_CTRL --> HGDO : disturbance estimation

SO3_NODELET --> SO3_ALGO

QUAD_SIM_NODE --> QUAD_DYN : step(dt)

SENS_SIM_CUDA --> CUDA_KERN
SENS_SIM_CUDA --> MAP_GEN

DG_BIN --> DG_CUDA
DG_BIN --> DG_MAPS

@enduml
```

**Source anchors:**
- `YOPO/cli.py` — CLI entry, all cmd_* functions
- `YOPO/schema.py` — YOPOConfig, DeployConfig, DatasetManifest
- `YOPO/policy/yopo_network.py` — YopoNetwork.forward()
- `YOPO/policy/yopo_trainer.py` — YopoTrainer (train / eval loop)
- `YOPO/policy/yopo_dataset.py` — YOPODataset (PyTorch Dataset)
- `YOPO/policy/primitive.py` — LatticePrimitive, LatticeParam
- `YOPO/policy/state_transform.py` — StateTransform
- `YOPO/policy/models/backbone.py` — ResNet18 的单通道深度包装器
- `YOPO/policy/models/head.py` — YopoHead (三层 1x1 卷积)
- `YOPO/loss/loss_function.py` — YOPOLoss (平滑度 + 安全性 + 引导 + 加速度)
- `YOPO/loss/esdf_gpu.py` — GPU/CPU EDT 回退
- `Controller/src/so3_control/src/network_control_node.cpp` — network_ctrl_node 入口
- `Controller/src/so3_control/src/NetworkControl.cpp` — NetworkControl (odom, cmd, 起降逻辑)
- `Controller/src/so3_control/src/SO3Control.cpp` — SO3Control (PD + 几何控制)
- `Controller/src/so3_control/include/so3_control/HGDO.h` — HGDO 扰动观测器
- `Controller/src/so3_quadrotor_simulator/src/quadrotor_simulator_so3.cpp` — SO3 四旋翼仿真节点
- `Simulator/src/src/test_simulator_cuda.cpp` — 传感器仿真器 CUDA 节点主函数
- `Simulator/src/include/maps.hpp` — 过程化环境生成
- `docker/data-gen/src/dataset_generator.cpp` — 离线数据集生成器入口
- `docker/data-gen/Dockerfile` — 数据生成的两阶段 Dockerfile
